<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Chicken Note</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="edn295">  295  Issy's act, producing a handkerchief, parodies Veronica's in wiping the face of Jesus with a cloth. As &lsquo;nosepaper&rsquo; her gift is also notepaper and, by extension, the &lsquo;Dear Maggy&rsquo; letter itself. We find various other letter overtones floating about: &lsquo;with my fondest and much left to tutor. X.X.X.X. It was heavily balledicted for young Fr Ml,&rsquo; &lsquo;till life's e'en,&rsquo; &lsquo;sester Maggy,&rsquo; &lsquo;funforall,&rsquo; &lsquo;hope to soon hear from you,&rsquo; and &lsquo;And thanks.&rsquo;  </div>
